vote.title: A public hearing to receive comments regarding a proposal to consider a request to change Locust Avenue between Gladewater Road and Aztec Drive, to “Frank Henderson Jr. Drive” and an ordinance granting the name change - NC190-001 - Financing: This action has no cost consideration to the City (see Fiscal Information for potential future costs)
